1. *Upao* je u veliku rupu. (He fell into a big hole.)
2. Pre nego što sam *upao* u spavaću sobu, uključio sam svetlo. (Before I entered the bedroom, I turned on the light.)
3. Nisam mogao da verujem kada sam *upao* u nevolju. (I couldn't believe it when I got into trouble.)
4. *Upao* sam u dugove i moram da tražim pomoć. (I got into debt and I need to ask for help.)
5. Zaboravio sam gde sam parkirao auto i sada ne mogu da ga nađem, čak sam *upao* u paniku. (I forgot where I parked my car and now I can't find it, I even panicked.)
6. Kada je video svog omiljenog glumca na ulici, *upao* je u oduševljenje. (When he saw his favorite actor on the street, he was thrilled.)
7. *Upao* sam u zamku lažnih obećanja. (I fell into the trap of false promises.)
8. Kada sam mu saopštio loše vesti, *upao* je u očajanje. (When I told him the bad news, he fell into despair.)
9. *Upao* je u neugodnu situaciju kada je zaboravio svoj govor. (He got into an awkward situation when he forgot his speech.)
10. *Upao* je u iskušenje da ukrade novac. (He was tempted to steal money.)